444
00:44:22,096 --> 00:44:23,498
Dia terjatuh.

445
00:44:54,901 --> 00:44:57,131
Apa? Mak, apa yg dia cakap?

446
00:44:57,303 --> 00:44:59,930
Dia nak awak hulurkan
roti dan mentega.

447
00:45:01,872 --> 00:45:04,533
- Saya tak tanya pada awak.
